	<div class="jumbotron text-center">
  <h1>Singapore</h1> 
  <p>Pack your bags to get ready for this short yet enthralling escapade to replenish your weary soul. Take our pocket-friendly Singapore tour package giving you the tour of the major tourist destinations in just 3 days. </p> 
</div> 
<div class="container">
	<h1>Itinerary</h1>
<pre><p><h2>Day 1</h2>- Arrival in Singapore
After your arrival in Singapore, you will be taken to the hotel by our representative.

Check-in and enjoy the rest of the day at your leisure for shopping or for resting.

Overnight at hotel.</p>


<p><h2>Day 2</h2>- Half Day City Tour Singapore
After breakfast in the morning, you will be embarking on a half day city tour of Singapore.

The tour will cover well-known attractions like Orchard Road, Suntec City and the Fountain of Wealth,
 Merlion Park, Singapore Flyer, Marina Bay Sands, Helix Bridge, Little India and China Town.

Also, you will be visiting the Thian Hock Temple.

Overnight at hotel.</p>


<p><h2>Day 3</h2> - Sentosa Island tour with transfers
After breakfast this morning, you will be leaving for your tour of the Sentosa Island.

Starting with the amazing cable car ride to the island, you will be getting an amazing aerial view of the 
entire island before you even set foot on the island.

You will be going to see the Underwater World, Dolphin Lagoon and the brilliant show of Wings of Time.

Overnight at hotel.</p>


<p><h2>Day 4</h2> - Check-out and departure
After breakfast this morning, you will be checking out of the hotel and get a transfer to the airport.

You will then catch a return flight, bringing the experience to an end.
</p>
</pre>

<h3> Ready for the trip?</h3>
